snippet.textDisplay: Wonderfully done in a very soothing fashion without going over the board by throwing in a lot of musical instruments. Although, the starting of the song messes with my head a bit because it's strikingly similar to Atif's 'Jeena Jeena' which I absolutely love. Momina did really well with the scale she was singing at. Looking forward to her next song! And finally, with RFAK singing a song, nothing can ever go wrong!
snippet.textOriginal: Wonderfully done in a very soothing fashion without going over the board by throwing in a lot of musical instruments. Although, the starting of the song messes with my head a bit because it's strikingly similar to Atif's 'Jeena Jeena' which I absolutely love. Momina did really well with the scale she was singing at. Looking forward to her next song! And finally, with RFAK singing a song, nothing can ever go wrong!
